transArray.content: The room was very clean and tidy, and the environment was very good.

We run and fight in the same sky, ushering in peach blossoms, sending away snowflakes, spring breeze awakening vitality everywhere, ushering in the summer when lotus blossoms bloom, ushering in the autumn when the rice is covered with golden dew, and finally ushering in the gentle Water you, I look forward to meeting you in all your glory. Love you Hanting
